OL,3,CCall for Guernsey officers to receive
OL,4,Cmore training in charging abuse
OL,5,Csuspects
OL,7,FAn email from a Guernsey Police
OL,8,Finspector has asked whether the
OL,9,Fforce's custody sergeants have
OL,10,Fadequate training to charge domestic
OL,11,Fabuse suspects.
OL,13,FThe email, written last year, was
OL,14,Fpenned by a senior detective inspector
OL,15,Fwho raised concerns that custody
OL,16,Fsergeants in Guernsey don't receive
OL,17,Fthe right level of legal training to
OL,18,Fcharge domestic abuse suspects
OL,19,Fproperly.
