OL,3,CCall for Guernsey officers to receive
OL,4,Cmore training in charging abuse
OL,5,Csuspects
OL,7,FGuernsey Police say that new
OL,8,Flegislation will introduce pre-charge
OL,9,Fbail conditions for offenders released
OL,10,Fwhilst under investigation, as well as
OL,11,Fthe use of domestic abuse protection
OL,12,Fnotices to prohibit contact between an
OL,13,Foffender and victim even if they have
OL,14,Finsufficient evidence to charge.
OL,16,FThey say the measures - alongside
OL,17,Fproposed changes to the force's
OL,18,Fcomplaints procedure - will help
OL,19,Fofficers make the right decisions.
