OL,4,Cmore training in charging abuse
OL,5,Csuspects
OL,7,FDeputy Chief Officer Bell adds: "The
OL,8,Flegislation is only the starting point
OL,9,Fof our journey to improve our
OL,10,Fawareness and response to domestic
OL,11,Fabuse and the wider concerns of
OL,12,Fviolence against women and young
OL,13,Fgirls."
OL,15,F"Last week we delivered the College of
OL,16,FPolicing "first responder domestic
OL,17,Fabuse training" to front-line staff
OL,18,Fand partners.
