OL,7,F"This may lead to charging decisions
OL,8,Fbeing made with this being at the
OL,9,Fforefront of minds.
OL,11,F"Thankfully, new legislation is set to
OL,12,Fshortly be brought in that will allow
OL,13,Ffor pre-charge bail conditions as an
OL,14,Foption."
